ing Programme of the European Atomic Energy Community (2021-2025). It is mandatory to submit a detailed budget table using the template available in the Submission system. Call documents Horizon Europe Work Programme 2025 Cluster 3 - Civil Security for SocietyHorizon Europe Work Programme 2025 Cluster 3 - Civil Security for Society(974kB) Contact National Contact Points for Horizon Europe Website',
